1
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,240
Meimei.

2
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,039
Meimei.

3
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,080
Meimei.

4
00:01:40,759 --> 00:01:41,440
Meimei.

5
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:44,440
Hello.

6
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,320
Delivery. Please sign.

7
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,580
I didn't buy anything.

8
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:51,720
There's no mistake.

9
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,850
It's for your house.

10
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,060
Where did you get this?

11
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,280
Someone put it on my vehicle

12
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,410
and gave me 100 yuan.

13
00:01:59,560 --> 00:01:59,890
Okay.

14
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:00,600
Got it.

15
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:01,600
Thanks.

16
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:36,980
Meimei.

17
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,400
Your daughter is quite well-behaved.

18
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,560
If you dare touch a hair on her head,

19
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,920
I will kill you.

20
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,920
Who are you?

21
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,560
What are you doing?

22
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,360
Don't touch her.

23
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,280
Calmed down now?

24
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,280
Can we talk?

25
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,660
I need you to do a few things for me.

26
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,380
As long as you finish them,

27
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,560
I promise your daughter will be unharmed.

28
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:26,240
I won't do anything for you.

29
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,200
I advise you to let my daughter go right now.

30
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:28,920
Otherwise,

31
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:31,040
I'll make you wish you were dead.

32
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:33,200
I've heard you have a fierce temper.

33
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,720
It's true.

34
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:38,520
But fortunately your daughter didn't inherit your flaws.

35
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,720
She's much easier to communicate with.

36
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,600
Don't.

37
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,480
Don't touch her.

38
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:44,840
She does exactly what she's told.

39
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,880
Okay.

40
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:47,040
I'll do it.

41
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,000
I'll do it.

42
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:51,040
You sound very reluctant.

43
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,820
But it doesn't matter.

44
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,970
I'll give you a little gift.

45
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:58,880
Let's see if it can change your attitude towards me.

46
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,640
We were just testing the equipment earlier.

47
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,760
We've implanted a bomb in your body.

48
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:26,160
The bomb is connected to the wristband.

49
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,640
When you're doing your task,

50
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,840
in case you get bored,

51
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,560
you'll be given a time limit.

52
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:33,880
If you don't finish the task in time,

53
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:36,640
or try to remove the bomb yourself,

54
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,560
or call the police,

55
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,360
it'll be a pity.

56
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,200
Bang!

57
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,020
You'll be blown to pieces.

58
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:46,760
And your daughter won't survive either.

59
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,880
But don't be nervous.

60
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:50,240
Believe in yourself.

61
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,640
You can definitely finish the task on time.

62
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:54,370
Then the bomb will be disarmed.

63
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,000
And you can reunite with your daughter.

64
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,680
How about we do a small task first,

65
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,960
so you can get used to the rules?

66
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,720
Taihua Square.

67
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:09,080
Take the phone I prepared for you.

68
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:11,760
I'll contact you then.

69
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,820
There's a trash can at eight o'clock.

70
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,320
There's a lunch box on it.

71
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:45,200
Do you see it?

72
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,370
Turn your head to your left.

73
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,890
Do you see the person walking towards you?

74
00:05:58,320 --> 00:06:00,080
Make him eat the stinky meat.

75
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,880
Are you crazy?

76
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,640
I can't do it.

77
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,200
Bro,

78
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,320
what are you doing?

79
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,360
Eat this.

80
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,320
I know I was wrong.

81
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:33,960
Shut up.

82
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,040
Listen to me.

83
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:38,040
Otherwise, I'll really shove this meat in your mouth.

84
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,760
When you run out later, pretend to throw up.

85
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,440
Make it look real.

86
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,170
Understand?

87
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,040
Understood.

88
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:46,490
Get lost.

89
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:59,320
You're breaking the rules before we even started.

90
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,440
Stop looking.

91
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:09,970
There's not much time left.

92
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,400
Let me use your mask, sir.

93
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:50,320
Driver.

94
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,000
Open the door.

95
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,760
Open the door. I want to get off.

96
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,200
Driver.

97
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,200
I can't stop until the next station.

98
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,040
What is this guy doing?

99
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,240
Driver, someone is making trouble.

100
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,560
Stop. Pull over.

101
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,690
What's going on?

102
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,380
What are you doing?

103
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:08,250
What are you guys doing?

104
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,620
What kind of society allows this?

105
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:18,090
Public morals are really going downhill.

106
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,559
It seems that if the pressure is great enough,

107
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,690
a person's bottom line can be crossed.

108
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,720
Your anger is understandable.

109
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,530
I won't hold it against you.

110
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:49,760
Then hurry up and let my daughter go.

111
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:52,340
That was just to let you get used to the rules.

112
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,690
The real mission hasn't even started yet.

113
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,200
Don't go easy on the upcoming missions.

114
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,360
Otherwise, you will have a hard time.

115
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:01,760
I'll give you more time for the new mission,

116
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:03,720
but the difficulty has also increased.

117
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,380
Hurry to Chang'an Square now.

118
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:07,420
Someone is waiting for you there.

119
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,680
Did you bring the stuff?
